
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <%= render 'layouts/head' %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="wrapper">
        <div id="headerwrap">
        <div id="header">
            <p><%= link_to image_tag('logo.png', :alt => "Brilliance Jobs"), root_path %></p>
        </div>
        </div>
	<div id = "navigationwrap">
	
        <%= render 'layouts/navigation'%>
	
	</div>
        <div id="contentwrap">
        <div id="content">
          <div class= "notice">
          <% flash.each do |key, value| %>
	    <div class = "flash <%= key %>"><%= value %></div>
          <% end %>
          <%= yield %>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>
        <% if !signed_in? %>
	<div id="rightcolumnwrap">
        <div id="rightcolumn">
	<h2>What we are?</h2>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer nec odio. Praesent libero. Sed cursus ante dapibus diam. Sed nisi. Nulla quis sem at nibh elementum imperdiet. Duis sagittis ipsum. Praesent mauris. Fusce nec tellus sed augue semper porta. Mauris massa. Vestibulum lacinia arcu eget nulla.</p>
	<div class = "btn">
	  <%= link_to('Sign up now!', signup_path, :class => "signup_button") %>
	</div>
        </div>
        </div>
        <% end %>
        <div id="footerwrap">
        <div id="footer">
            <p>This is the Footer</p>
        </div>
        </div>
        <% if Rails.env.development? %>
        <div id = "debugwrap">
          <div id = "debug">
            <h3>[params] Debugging Information</h3>
            <%= debug(params) %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% end %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

